&lt;h3 id=&#34;Cell-Array&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Cell-Array&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Cell Array&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Cell Array&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Another method of storing heterogeneous data&lt;br&gt;Similar to matrix but each entry contains different type of data&lt;br&gt;Declared using {}&lt;/p&gt;
